00:24:09,320 --> 00:24:10,400
ENCOUNTERING A NEW ERA, A NEW PERSON

404
00:24:10,480 --> 00:24:11,860
…and leave empty-handed.

405
00:24:12,360 --> 00:24:13,530
I see.

406
00:24:13,610 --> 00:24:16,570
That was Assemblyman Oh's principle
when it comes to politics.

407
00:24:16,660 --> 00:24:17,910
If he declares candidacy, that is.

408
00:24:18,870 --> 00:24:23,250
Let's look forward to seeing
the rise of a new political leader.

409
00:24:23,330 --> 00:24:26,630
