418
00:24:51,650 --> 00:24:55,450
I already know the hit-and-run accident
and suicide were in the contract.

419
00:24:55,990 --> 00:24:58,570
As soon as I received
a huge amount of money in the bank,

420
00:24:58,660 --> 00:25:00,580
I got a call about my husband's death.

421
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:03,910
And the day after that,
I received his suicide note.

422
00:25:04,660 --> 00:25:06,250
It was all written there.

423
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:10,460
Where he got the money,
who made him do it,

424
00:25:10,540 --> 00:25:13,090
and why he had to take his own life.

425
00:25:14,130 --> 00:25:15,420
Where is

426
00:25:16,220 --> 00:25:17,800
Mr. Yang's suicide note?

427
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:20,890
If you lay a finger on me or my child,

428
00:25:22,180 --> 00:25:24,560
that note will be sent to the police.

429
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:27,390
I must save myself too.

430
00:25:32,730 --> 00:25:33,730
All right.

431
00:25:35,190 --> 00:25:37,200
Would you like to continue watching?

432
00:25:38,570 --> 00:25:41,740
It took me a lot of effort

433
00:25:41,830 --> 00:25:44,160
to find all these.

434
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:45,250
Do you know that?

435
00:25:47,750 --> 00:25:49,330
Apparently, at the time of the accident,

436
00:25:49,420 --> 00:25:53,130
