437
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:55,550
How does that make any sense?

438
00:25:55,630 --> 00:25:57,420
He had just cut ties with his mother,

439
00:25:57,510 --> 00:25:59,090
but managed to sleep peacefully afterward?

440
00:25:59,180 --> 00:26:03,890
Does this mean
Kang-ho is the worst bastard in history?

441
00:26:04,890 --> 00:26:07,640
Or did someone slip him

442
00:26:07,730 --> 00:26:09,810
sleeping pills or something?

443
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:11,310
Oh, right.

444
00:26:12,810 --> 00:26:16,230
The day before the accident, your daughter

445
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:20,030
