446
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:21,110
Mr. Song!

447
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:23,620
Right, I enjoyed your show.

448
00:26:23,700 --> 00:26:25,330
You were eloquent.

449
00:26:25,410 --> 00:26:28,160
