454
00:26:58,360 --> 00:26:59,610
Choi Hae-sik?

455
00:27:00,320 --> 00:27:01,610
Choi… Who?

456
00:27:01,700 --> 00:27:03,070
Back in 1987,

457
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,570
during the urban improvement,

458
00:27:04,660 --> 00:27:07,580
the man who was running
a pig farm in Bongu-dong.

459
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:10,330
That Choi Hae-sik.

460
00:27:10,410 --> 00:27:13,210
Goodness, I don't even remember
someone I met yesterday.

461
00:27:13,290 --> 00:27:15,500
A man from 30 years ago?
Anyway, what about him?

462
00:27:15,590 --> 00:27:18,760
Do you know how my daughter
came to meet Choi Kang-ho?

463
00:27:20,090 --> 00:27:22,510
My daughter was arrested by him

464
00:27:22,590 --> 00:27:24,640
for carrying illegal drugs.

465
00:27:25,300 --> 00:27:26,680
It was odd, so I checked.

466
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:29,640
But they didn't receive
any order or report

467
00:27:29,720 --> 00:27:31,390
regarding illegal drugs.

468
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:33,350
That's right.

469
00:27:34,060 --> 00:27:36,560
He approached her on purpose.

470
00:27:38,480 --> 00:27:39,530
I'm sure

471
00:27:40,570 --> 00:27:42,570
