he is Choi Hae-sik's son?

490
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:42,460
That's crazy.

491
00:28:42,550 --> 00:28:43,670
Are you saying

492
00:28:43,760 --> 00:28:46,510
you already knew who Choi Kang-ho was?

493
00:28:49,010 --> 00:28:50,640
Look, Mr. Oh.

494
00:28:51,390 --> 00:28:52,770
Do you really think

495
00:28:52,850 --> 00:28:55,730
I wouldn't have checked
before I took him in

496
00:28:56,390 --> 00:28:58,100
to do the dirtiest of jobs for me?

497
00:29:02,280 --> 00:29:05,860
She said she'd give me drugs,
but it was a lie!

498
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:09,280
So…

499
00:29:10,910 --> 00:29:12,620
I killed her.

500
00:29:19,580 --> 00:29:21,340
No, Chairman Song.

501
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:24,260
I didn't hear anything.
Please, sir. Don't kill me!

502
00:29:24,340 --> 00:29:27,840
Jung Jong-gu, the defendant and owner
of a street tteokbokki stall,

503
00:29:27,930 --> 00:29:30,510
went to an alley nearby
to return a lipstick

504
00:29:30,600 --> 00:29:31,970
Woo Mi-jeong had left behind,

505
00:29:32,060 --> 00:29:34,100
where he found her dead.

506
00:29:34,810 --> 00:29:37,520
The defendant checked to see
if she was conscious,

507
00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:39,690
then a passerby saw it and made a report.

508
00:29:39,770 --> 00:29:43,110
